# Standalone eMMC profile — production. The embedded busybox initramfs from
# tc8-rootfs handles slot-aware root mount, so we hand off with rw rootwait and
# no explicit root=.
#
# Display rotation: kernel `video=DSI-1:rotate=270` makes wlroots/cage see
# a 1280x800 landscape output; cage `-r` (single, set in tc8-rootfs's
# kiosk.service) gives the final viewing orientation. Touch transform
# follows automatically. Verified end-to-end with tools/touch.html.
KERNEL_CMDLINE="console=tty0 console=ttymxc1,115200 earlycon=ec_imx6q,0x30890000,115200 keep_bootcon panic=10 rw rootwait fw_devlink=permissive video=DSI-1:rotate=270 vt.global_cursor_default=0"
